git = track changes in our code and lets us easily undo our changes 
-very useful for bigger projects
repository = a folder where changes are being tracked
git config user.name "Your Name"  # set the name associated with your commits
git config user.email "ur email"  # set the email associated with your commits
git init  # initialize a new git repository in the current folder
git status  # check the status of your repository
git add filename  # stage a specific file for commit  

